<bibRefCitation author="Latreille, P. A." box="[611,770,1480,1503]" pageId="52" pageNumber="53" refId="ref57975" refString="Latreille, P. A. (1807) Genera Crustaceorum et Insectorum Secundum Ordinem Naturalem in Familias Disposita, Iconibus Exemplisque Plurimis Explicata, volume 3, Amand Koenig, Parisiis et Argentorati, 259 pp." type="book" year="1807">Latreille, 1807</bibRefCitation>
